object.customQuery:
SELECT distinct provider.SystemId, provider.ParentId, provider.CMMContainer, provider.Id, provider.UpdateCount, provider.UpdateUser, provider.UpdateTimestamp, provider.Version, provider.IndexName, provider.ProviderTypeCd, provider.StatusCd, provider.StatusDt, provider.ProviderNumber, provider.NewProviderRef, provider.NewProviderDt, provider.Comments, provider.PaymentPreferenceCd, provider.PreferredDeliveryMethod, provider.ServicePortalContactNotes, provider.ProviderOnCommissionPlan, provider.CombinePaymentInd, provider.NotificationMethod, provider.OkToAssign, provider.AdjusterState, provider.RowId 
FROM
 provider
where systemid in (select SystemId from advrxxchangedbeans where concat(adddt,addtm)>='$$M_StartDt' and concat(adddt,addtm) <='$$M_EndDt' and
 cmmcontainer='Provider')
